import React from 'react';
import { Tabs, TabList, Tab, TabPanels, TabPanel, Card, Image, Stack, Heading, Text } from '@chakra-ui/react';

const EventsDiscovery = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Heading fontFamily='Montserrat, sans-serif' fontWeight='bold' color='white' fontSize='50px' textAlign='center' mt={8} mb={4}>
                Events
            </Heading>

            <Tabs variant='enclosed' colorScheme='purple'>
                <TabList bg='purple.200' borderRadius='xl' p={4} mb={4}>
                    <Tab _selected={{ color: 'white', bg: 'purple.600' }} _focus={{ boxShadow: 'none' }} _hover={{ bg: 'purple.500' }} mr={2} fontSize='xl'>Dance</Tab>
                    <Tab _selected={{ color: 'white', bg: 'purple.600' }} _focus={{ boxShadow: 'none' }} _hover={{ bg: 'purple.500' }} mr={2}>Music - Classical</Tab>
                </TabList>
                <TabPanels>
                    <TabPanel>
                        <Stack spacing={8}>
                            <Card direction={{ base: 'column', sm: 'row' }} overflow='hidden' variant='elevated' bg="rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)" maxW="97%" padding="20px" borderRadius={"50px"}>
                                <Image
                                    objectFit='cover'
                                    maxW={{ base: '100%', sm: '50%' }}
                                    src='/p5.png'
                                    alt='Logo of Brand'
                                />
                                <Stack>
                                    <Heading> Event 1</Heading>
                                    <Text py='4' fontSize="18px" fontFamily='Montserrat, sans-serif' fontWeight="500">
                                        Event description goes here...
                                    </Text>
                                </Stack>
                            </Card>
                            {/* Repeat similar Card structure for other events */}
                        </Stack>
                    </TabPanel>
                    <TabPanel>
                        <Stack spacing={8}>
                            <Card direction={{ base: 'column', sm: 'row' }} overflow='hidden' variant='elevated' bg="rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)" maxW="97%" padding="20px" borderRadius={"50px"}>
                                <Image
                                    objectFit='cover'
                                    maxW={{ base: '100%', sm: '50%' }}
                                    src='/p5.png'
                                    alt='Logo of Brand'
                                />
                                <Stack>
                                    <Heading> Event 2</Heading>
                                    <Text py='4' fontSize="18px" fontFamily='Montserrat, sans-serif' fontWeight="500">
                                        Event description goes here...
                                    </Text>
                                </Stack>
                            </Card>
                            {/* Repeat similar Card structure for other events */}
                        </Stack>
                    </TabPanel>
                </TabPanels>
            </Tabs>
        </>
    )
}

export default EventsDiscovery;
